  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://img.soy-chile.cl/Fotos/2012/12/07/file_20121207205111.jpg\" /></p>\n<div id=\"cke_pastebin\">\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p766836\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tBut first, in 2003, a Chilean woman called Bernarda Gallardo saw a story in her local paper which changed her life. A dead baby girl had been found dumped on the local rubbish tip, literally thrown out with the household waste. The <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/article\" target=\"_blank\">article</a> had such an impact on Bernarda that she made it her mission to give that baby a proper <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/burial\" target=\"_blank\">burial</a>. The process was far from <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/straightforward\" target=\"_blank\">straightforward</a>. It turned out to be long and <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bureaucratic\" target=\"_blank\">bureaucratic</a> as a recent film based on Bernarda's story reveals.</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\t&quot;Are you a member of her family?&quot;<br />\n\t\t&quot;No.&quot;<br />\n\t\t&quot;Leave your number with my secretary.&quot;<br />\n\t\t&quot;I will come on Monday and then on the following Monday. And if nothing happens, I will keep coming back.&quot;<br />\n\t\t&quot;You will be wasting your time and mine. There's nothing that can be done.&quot;<br />\n\t\t&quot;There's always a solution.&quot;</p>\n\t<p style=\"line-height: 25px;\">\n\t\tWell, Bernarda's <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/determination\" target=\"_blank\">determination</a> to care for this unwanted baby had its roots in her own background. For Outlook, Jane Chambers went to meet her in the southern Chilean town of Puerto Montt, where she lives.<br />\n\t